short_description: This US-SJSZ55/110 model line is adapted to the production of decorative foam plastic profiles. The motor of the line is 22 kW, the maximum width of the produced profile is 240 mm, and the production capacity is up to 100 kg/h.

long_description:
This US-SJSZ55/110 model line is adapted to the production of decorative foam plastic profiles. The motor of the line is 22 kW, the maximum width of the produced profile is 240 mm, and the production capacity is up to 100 kg/h.

 

 

Basic parameters
Model US-SJSZ55/110
Extruder motor power 22 kW
Down-stream machine YF240
Product width 240 mm
Capacity 100 kg/hour
